@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yitifs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.30 + 0.61)
    v0 = (v1 / wp.sin(0.35))
    tmp = 0.10
    v1 = 0.33
    v1 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v1 + 0.59 * v2 + 0.59)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.62 / v2 + 0.76)) + (wp.exp(v2 + 0.87) - (v1 + 0.96 / tmp + 0.24)))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.21) + v2) + (tmp * (tmp + 0.28 * v0 + 0.45)))
    data[tid] = v0
